alerts.alertHeaderText: State Elevator 974 (Bowdoin platform to Congress Street, 60 State Street) unavailable
alerts.alertDescriptionText: To exit, travel down the nearby ramp to the Orange Line Oak Grove platform, turn left, then use State Elevator 967 or 802 to access the Wonderland platform. Continue along the Wonderland platform to the 53 State St lobby and use State Elevator 975 to access the street. To board, cross State St, then proceed to the station entrance at 53 State St and use State Elevator 975 to access the Wonderland platform. At the Wonderland platform, turn left and proceed to the end of the platform (follow signs for Orange Line and Government Center/Bowdoin) and use State Elevator 967 or 802 to access the Orange Line Oak Grove platform. At the Oak Grove platform, turn right and travel up the nearby ramp to the Blue Line Bowdoin platform.
